skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to a week of fun happenings in Mansfield, Texas. Just say "What's my flash briefing". You can say "Stop" to exit anytime.

Please enable this Skill within your Alexa app. You can add it into your daily flash briefings, it doesn't have to replace your current briefings.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
